---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pageTitle: "Privacy Policy"
metaDescription: "Mainstreet Benchmark privacy policy. We don't collect personal data, require registration, or sell information. AdSense may set cookies."
canonicalPath: /privacy-policy/
---

{% block schema %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Privacy Policy", "item": "{{ site.url }}/privacy-policy/" }
  ]
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
  <ol>
    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</li>
  </ol>
</nav>

<article class="legal-page">
  <div class="container">

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: {{ site.dataLastModified }}</p>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>What We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Mainstreet Benchmark does not require registration or collect personal information to use
        the calculator. You can calculate your business valuation, run What-If scenarios, and access
        all industry data without creating an account or providing any personal information.
      </p>
      <p>
        The calculator inputs you enter (industry, SDE, revenue, trend, owner involvement, customer
        concentration) are processed entirely in your browser. These values are not transmitted to
        our servers or stored anywhere.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        If analytics are enabled on this site (see our <a href="/about/">About page</a> for current
        status), we use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to collect aggregate, anonymized data about page
        visits, session duration, and general usage patterns. GA4 data is subject to
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        GA4 does not receive calculator inputs or any personally identifiable information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        This site displays ads served by Google AdSense. AdSense uses cookies to serve relevant
        advertisements based on your prior visits to this and other websites. Google's use of
        advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visit to this
        site and/or other sites on the internet. You can opt out of personalized advertising by
        visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Mainstreet Benchmark itself does not set cookies. Third-party services used by this site
        (Google Analytics, Google AdSense) may set cookies as described in their respective privacy
        policies. No cookie consent banner is required for cookies set entirely by third parties
        in jurisdictions where this site operates, but users in the EU/EEA may see cookie notices
        required by their local law.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        This site contains links to external resources including BizBuySell, Google, and other
        third-party websites. Mainstreet Benchmark is not responsible for the privacy practices
        or content of external sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any
        third-party sites you visit.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Because we do not collect personally identifiable information, there is no personal data
        to retain or delete. If you have questions about data held by third-party services (Google
        Analytics, AdSense), contact those services directly through their privacy settings.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is intended for adults (18+) preparing to sell or buy a business. We do not
        knowingly collect information from children under 13.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy periodically. Changes will be reflected in the "Last updated"
        date at the top of this page.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this privacy policy: <a href="mailto:{{ site.contactEmail }}">{{ site.contactEmail }}</a>
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</article>

{% endblock %}
